snippet.title: Guilty Gear: The Missing Link (PC) - SOL BADGUY Gameplay Playthrough
snippet.description:
Playthrough / Longplay / Gameplay playing as SOL BADGUY.

🎮 Learn the moves of the characters in the GG ML playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLOO2o6Kew2GNEJB-9_Kd-ZEk-oQH2p3S7

0:07 - Sol vs. Kliff
0:42 - Sol vs. Millia
1:22 - Sol vs. Axl
2:05 - Sol vs. Dr. Baldhead
2:47 - Sol vs. Zato
4:15 - Sol vs. Potemkin
5:48 - Sol vs. May
7:06 - Sol vs. Chipp
8:44 - Sol vs. Ky
11:21 - Sol vs. Testament
13:50 - Sol vs. Justice
15:11 - Sol Ending
17:18 - Sol vs. Baiken

Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5YuXeo6i8QQ&list=PL_YL558gxlL_SsFdw5MOJ1QjgLiM8sg79

There are the ending credits between the fight between Justice and Baiken, which was purposely removed from the video.

Release data:
Guilty Gear (2019) / (1998 - Original Release for Playstation)
Genre: Fighting
Platform: PC  (Steam)
Developer: Arc System Works

Recorded at 60 fps with Live Gamer Portable 2 - GC510, 60fps 1080p.

#solbadguy #guiltygear #themissinglink
